## 2. Architecture Pattern: MVVM + Clean + Coordinator

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│           Navigation Layer                   │
│   AppCoordinator  (route state machine)      │
│   AppDependencyContainer  (DI / factories)   │
└────────────────────┬─────────────────────────┘
                     │ creates / routes to
┌────────────────────▼─────────────────────────┐
│            Presentation Layer                │
│   SwiftUI Views  +  ViewModels               │
│   (CompanionViewModel, AuthViewModel,        │
│    OnboardingViewModel)                      │
└────────────────────┬─────────────────────────┘
                     │ calls / observes
┌────────────────────▼─────────────────────────┐
│             Service Layer                    │
│   AccessoryManager  BLEService               │
│   LocalDeviceAccessory  ExternalSDKAccessory │
│   PrivacyPipelineService  PIIScrubber        │
│   CloudAgentService  AudioService            │
│   AudioCaptureService  SpeechRecognitionSvc  │
│   AuthenticationService  PrivacyMetricsStore │
└────────────────────┬─────────────────────────┘
                     │ uses
┌────────────────────▼─────────────────────────┐
│              Model Layer                     │
│   Pure Swift structs / enums (Sendable)      │
│   No UIKit, no framework imports             │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Rules:**
- ViewModels are `@Observable` (Swift 5.9+ macro)
- Services are injected via `AppDependencyContainer` factory methods
- All async work uses Swift structured concurrency (`async/await`, `Task`, `AsyncStream`)
- Services are `actor` or `@MainActor final class` — no Combine, no RxSwift

