## 6. Session State Machine
```swift
enum SessionState: Equatable, Sendable {
    case idle               // No wearable connected
    case scanning           // startDiscovery() in progress
    case connected          // Wearable connected, ready
    case receivingImage     // Receiving JPEG chunks (BLE mode only)
    case processingPrivacy  // On-device privacy pipeline running
    case requestingStory    // POST to cloud agent in progress
    case encodingAudio      // TTS synthesis running
    case sendingAudio       // Writing audio to wearable
    case recordingAudio     // Mic capture + live transcription active
    case transcribingAudio  // Final transcription pass running
    case error(String)      // Error with description
}
```

`isConnected` returns `true` for all states except `.idle`, `.scanning`, and `.error`.

