## 15. Privacy Metrics (`PrivacyMetricsStore`)

`PrivacyMetricsStore` is an `actor` that accumulates `PrivacyMetricsEvent` records in memory and provides dissertation-ready evidence.

### `PrivacyMetricsEvent` fields
| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `facesDetected` / `facesBlurred` | Proof faces are always blurred |
| `objectsDetected` | Object count per run |
| `tokensScrubbedFromTranscript` | PII tokens redacted |
| `rawDataTransmitted` | Always `false` — privacy invariant |
| `pipelineLatencyMs` | Total on-device time |
| `faceDetectMs`, `blurMs`, `yoloMs`, `sceneClassifyMs`, `sttMs`, `piiScrubMs` | Per-stage breakdown |
| `timestamp` | `CFAbsoluteTime` of pipeline start |

### Queries
- `averageLatency()` — mean pipeline latency
- `privacySanitisationRate()` — fraction of runs where `rawDataTransmitted == false` (target: 1.0)
- `totalFacesDetected()` / `totalFacesBlurred()` — cumulative counts
- `exportCSV()` — 13-column CSV string for dissertation appendix

