        ▼
CompanionViewModel.captureScene()
  → accessoryManager.activeAccessory.sendCommand("CAPTURE")
        │
        ▼ (iPhone camera path)
LocalDeviceAccessory.captureOneFrame()
  → AVCapturePhotoOutput.capturePhoto(with:delegate:)
  → delegate.photoOutput(_:didFinishProcessingPhoto:)
  → imageYielder.yield(jpegData)
        │
        ▼ (BLE path)
BLEService sends "CAPTURE" command to AiSee
  → AiSee captures image, sends chunked JPEG via IMAGE_DATA_TX NOTIFY
  → BLEService.peripheral(_:didUpdateValueFor:) parses chunks
  → ChunkBuffer.add(chunk) → when complete: imageYielder.yield(reassembledData)
        │
        ▼
imageStreamTask receives jpegData
  → CompanionViewModel.runDetectionPreview(jpegData:)
        │
        ▼
PrivacyPipelineService.runDebugDetection(jpegData:)
  → Stage 1+2: VNDetectFaceRectanglesRequest → CIGaussianBlur(σ=30) per face
  → Stage 3:   VNCoreMLRequest (YOLO11n) → [DetectionResult] with bounding boxes
  → returns (blurredJPEG, detections, metrics)
        │
        ▼
CompanionViewModel:
  capturedImageData = blurredJPEG
  sceneDetections   = detections
  isShowingScenePreview = true
  metricsStore.record(metrics)
        │
        ▼
[Full pipeline: when story is requested]
PrivacyPipelineService.process(jpegData:childAge:audioData:)
  async let objects    = detectObjects(in: blurredImage)       // YOLO11n
  async let scene      = classifyScene(in: blurredImage)       // VNClassifyImageRequest
  async let transcript = recognizeSpeech(audioData: audioData) // SFSpeechRecognizer (on-device)
  → PIIScrubber.scrub(transcript)
  → ScenePayload { objects, scene, transcript, childAge, sessionId, query, timestamp }
  → PipelineResult { payload, metrics }
        │
        ▼
CloudAgentService.requestStory(payload:)
  → POST <cloudAgentURL>/story { objects, scene, transcript, childAge, … }
  → StoryResponse { storyText }
        │
        ▼
AudioService.generateAndEncodeAudio(from: storyText)
  → AVSpeechSynthesizer.write(utterance) { buffer → accumulate PCM }
  → returns PCM Float32 Data (~22050 Hz, mono)
        │
        ▼
accessoryManager.activeAccessory.sendAudio(pcmData)
  iPhone path:  AVAudioPlayerNode.scheduleBuffer → built-in speaker
  BLE path:     write 508-byte chunks to AUDIO_DATA_RX (20ms pacing)
        │
        ▼
timeline.insert(TimelineEntry(sceneObjects:, storySnippet:), at: 0)
sessionState = .connected
