## 18. Privacy Guarantees
| Data | Treatment |
|------|-----------|
| Raw JPEG from wearable | Discarded in memory after `PrivacyPipelineService.process()` returns |
| Face bounding boxes | Used only to drive blur, never stored or transmitted |
| Blurred JPEG | Displayed in-app for debug preview only; never stored to disk or sent to network |
| Voice audio | Processed on-device via `SFSpeechRecognizer(requiresOnDeviceRecognition: true)` |
| Transcript text | PII-scrubbed via `PIIScrubber` before inclusion in `ScenePayload` |
| `ScenePayload` sent to cloud | Contains only anonymous labels and age — no raw sensor data |
| Cloud response (story text) | Temporary in-memory only, passed to TTS, discarded |
| TTS audio | PCM Data in memory only; not persisted to disk |
| `PrivacyMetricsEvent.rawDataTransmitted` | Always `false` — enforced by pipeline invariant, auditable via `PrivacyMetricsStore` |

***
## 19. Error Handling
All errors surface via `CompanionViewModel.lastError` / `sessionState = .error(msg)` and are displayed in `CameraTabView`'s error banner.

| Failure | Behaviour |
|---------|-----------|
| Wearable permission denied | `WearableError.permissionDenied` → error banner, state → `.idle` |
| BLE disconnected mid-transfer | `ChunkBuffer.reset()`, state → `.idle`, show reconnect button |
| CoreML model load failure | Graceful fallback: scene-classification-only; warning logged at startup |
| Cloud request timeout (> 15s) | `URLSession` timeout → `CloudError` → error banner, state → `.connected` |
| Cloud 4xx/5xx | `CloudError.unexpectedStatusCode(code)` → display error |
| Audio synthesis failure | `AudioError.synthesisFailed` → display error |
| Speech recognizer unavailable | Logged; `transcript` remains `nil`; pipeline continues without voice |

