## 21. Next Steps — Story Generation (Foundation Models + Cloud Agent)
The architecture is designed to extend into a **co-creative turn-based story generation** mode. The planned additions are:

```
iPhone (on-device)                    Cloud Agent (Tier 3)
──────────────────                    ────────────────────
Apple Foundation Models API           Multi-turn story agent
  - Structured output                   - Maintains story state
  - Local scene enrichment              - Character + arc continuity
  - Offline-capable first turn          - Cloud TTS (optional)
        │
        ▼
ScenePayload + storyContext (turn N)
  → POST /story/continue
        │
        ▼
StoryResponse { storyText, storyContext, turnNumber }
```

Key model fields to add to `ScenePayload` / `StoryResponse` for turn-based support:
- `storyContext: String?` — serialised prior story state
- `turnNumber: Int` — current turn index
- `speakerTurn: String` — `"child"` | `"companion"` (who speaks next)

